	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- Regarding <a href="http://famitracker.shoodot.net/forum/posts.php?id=390&amp;pid=4250#4250" class="postlink">this topic</a> on FamiTracker forums, the guy says the PAL plays slower than the NTSC. Well, yes, PAL uses 50Hz and NTSC 60Hz. By the way, for my best, the tempo and music pitch <strong>does not</strong> change.
<br />
<br />- Just to be sure I'm <strong>not</strong> crazy, is his argument wrong? o.O

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


